reviewText: I found this very DVD enjoyable and informative. Van Auken does an excellent job. I plan to visit these sites soon and needed an overview of what to see. Well done. I wish it had been longer!

This DVD is definitely worth the money, and your time. I've always loved the Cayce material, and walked away from this work with a lot of new information. It's a nice addition to anyone's mystical/metaphysical/esoteric DVD collection.
